All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
CSVReader
The CSVReader class is responsible for reading satellite and debris data from a CSV file and populating a TrackingSystem with the parsed objects.
Debris
The Debris class represents a space object classified as orbital debris.
DebrisDensityAnalysis
The DebrisDensityAnalysis class provides functionality to analyze and report the density of space debris across different orbit types.
ImpactAnalysis
 
LoggerUtility
The LoggerUtility class provides a simple logging utility to record system events and messages into a log file with timestamps.
MissionControl
The MissionControl class represents a mission control center responsible for managing and interacting with the tracking system of space objects.
RocketBody
The RocketBody class represents a rocket body in space.
RunSimulation
The RunSimulation class serves as the entry point for the space object tracking simulation.
Satellite
The Satellite class represents a satellite in space.
SpaceObject
The SpaceObject class serves as an abstract representation of a tracked object in space.
TrackingSystem
The TrackingSystem class manages a list of tracked space objects.
UnknownObject
The UnknownObject class represents an unknown space object.
